@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #f9f9f9
  BorderColor #555
}

title Doggy - UI State Diagram

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state Analyzing
state ResultDisplayed
state ErrorDisplayed

Idle --> Analyzing : user submits image
Analyzing --> ResultDisplayed : API returns success\nset result, clear error
Analyzing --> ErrorDisplayed : API returns error\nset error, clear result
ResultDisplayed --> Analyzing : user submits another image
ErrorDisplayed --> Analyzing : user retries with another image

@enduml
